---
title: Pork, Pear & Blue Cheese Burger with Wedges and Lemony Walnut Salad
description: We love good Pork, Pear & Cheese Burger with Wedges and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-pear-blue-cheese-burger-f03707a7-ac55e4e7.jpg
